{"words":[{"word":"zhezhi","count":2},{"word":"thank","count":2},{"word":"i've","count":2},{"word":"paintings","count":2},{"word":"hehe","count":2},{"word":"painting","count":2},{"word":"researchers","count":1},{"word":"taken","count":1},{"word":"good","count":1},{"word":"care","count":1},{"word":"chat","count":1},{"word":"hurt","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"rover","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"freeing","count":1},{"word":"nightmares","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"soft","count":1},{"word":"gentle","count":1},{"word":"outside","count":1},{"word":"boundaries","count":1},{"word":"crossed","count":1},{"word":"tougher","count":1},{"word":"anyone","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"owe","count":1},{"word":"apology","count":1},{"word":"forgive","count":1},{"word":"obsessed","count":1},{"word":"wanting","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"caused","count":1},{"word":"trouble","count":1},{"word":"pain","count":1},{"word":"injuries","count":1},{"word":"managed","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"stop","count":1},{"word":"obsession","count":1},{"word":"imitating","count":1},{"word":"heh","count":1},{"word":"maybe","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"meant","count":1},{"word":"painter","count":1},{"word":"begin","count":1},{"word":"create","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"ironic","count":1},{"word":"trying","count":1},{"word":"imitate","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"years","count":1},{"word":"apart","count":1},{"word":"anymore","count":1},{"word":"bringing","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Zhezhi... It's been a while.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"The researchers have taken good care of me. A chat won't hurt. And you must be... the Rover?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"I heard about everything you did. Thank you for freeing me from those nightmares.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"You know what, Zhezhi? You may seem soft and gentle on the outside, but if your boundaries are crossed, I think you can be tougher than anyone else.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"And... I still owe you an apology.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Forgive me. Because I was so obsessed with wanting to be you... to be <i>better</i> than you, I've caused you so much trouble...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"...The pain of these injuries managed to put a stop to my obsession with imitating your paintings.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Heh. Maybe... I was never meant to be a painter to begin with...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Hehe, see...? Only you can create a painting with such life. I still have a long way to go.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"I... Hehe... How ironic. I've been trying to imitate you for so many years that now I can't even tell my own paintings apart anymore.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"...Thank you for bringing me this painting... Really.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000}]}